item.description: 1 2 3 # Initialize Otter import otter grader = otter.Notebook("lab01.ipynb") Lab 01 Welcome to the first lab of Data 100! This lab is meant to help you familiarize yourself with JupyterHub, review Python and numpy, and introduce you to matplotlib, a Python visualization library. To receive credit for a lab, answer all questions correctly and submit before the deadline. This lab is due Tuesday, January 25 at 11:59 PM.
